Package com.osoc6.OSOC6.webhook

Enum Class QuestionKey

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<QuestionKey>
com.osoc6.OSOC6.webhook.QuestionKey
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<QuestionKey>, Constable
public enum QuestionKey extends Enum<QuestionKey>
This enum holds all questions used to fill in a new Student. Every QuestionKey enum object has it's own addToStudent method which extracts the answer from it's given form field and adds it to the given student.
